5. Classification Stability

Given the proposed final state C:

Hypatia tests:
	â€¢	Does C follow from eliminating all S under R & E?
	â€¢	Is C stable under small perturbations of F/E?
	â€¢	Is C exclusive (no other classifications survive)?
	â€¢	Does C contradict known theorems, bounds, or invariants?

Hypatia confirms classification or returns:
	â€¢	â€œClassification not forcedâ€
	â€¢	â€œAlternative structures surviveâ€
	â€¢	â€œClassification contradicts Flow invariantsâ€

