5. Hypatia Zero-Types (New Hammer Classes)

Hypatia introduces three important zero-types:

Zero-Type	Meaning
Execution Zero	Can this flow actually run without breaking invariants?
Monotonicity Zero	Does the energy functional behave monotonically along real flows?
Surgery Zero	Are the proposed surgeries topologically/analytically legal?

These are used to reject pathological reasoning early.

